targets.rawSql:
SELECT 
	"time",
	updated
FROM 
	(SELECT
	  updated AS "time",
	  extract(epoch from updated - interval '7 hours') AS utc_time,
	  to_char(updated,'yyyy-mm-dd HH24:MI') as updated
	FROM dashboard
	WHERE title = 'test generate'
	) AS fd
ORDER BY 1

SELECT 
	"time",
	u."name" AS "name" 
FROM 
	(SELECT 
		updated AS "time",
		extract(epoch from updated - interval '7 hours') AS utc_time,
		updated_by
	FROM dashboard 
	WHERE title = 'test generate'
	) AS fd
LEFT JOIN "user" as u
  ON fd.updated_by = u.id
ORDER BY 1
